      <title>印度宗教集会发生踩踏事件 恐造成数人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/several-feared-killed-at-stampede-in-india-s-religious-gathering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地媒体报道，印度世界最大的宗教集会上发生踩踏事件，造成多人受伤，数人恐已死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/several-feared-killed-at-stampede-in-india-s-religious-gathering</guid>
