    <item>
      <title>特朗普冻结拜登绿色银行、电动汽车税收抵免等计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-freeze-targets-biden-s-green-bank-ev-tax-credits-and-more</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在特朗普政府下令的政府支出冻结措施下，用于清洁能源项目的 4000 亿美元绿色银行和广受欢迎的电动汽车消费者税收抵免等项目都是需要审查的项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-freeze-targets-biden-s-green-bank-ev-tax-credits-and-more</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 01:07:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥批准部分外援豁免，以暂停特朗普的支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/rubio-approves-some-foreign-aid-exemptions-amid-trump-s-halt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统发布行政命令暂停并重新评估所有外国发展援助引发世界各地援助团体的强烈抗议后，国务卿马尔科·卢比奥批准了部分紧急粮食援助和工资豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/rubio-approves-some-foreign-aid-exemptions-amid-trump-s-halt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 00:42:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国官员警告称，入侵使刚果城市戈马陷入危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/m23-invasion-plunges-drc-city-goma-into-crisis-un-official-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国高级官员周二在安理会紧急会议上表示，刚果民主共和国东部城市戈马正遭受卢旺达支持的叛军袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/m23-invasion-plunges-drc-city-goma-into-crisis-un-official-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 00:32:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本新贵政党提出 370 亿美元支持首相石破茂的预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/japan-upstart-party-has-37-billion-offer-to-back-prime-minister-ishiba-s-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相石破茂的目标是让年度预算获得通过 — — 这也许决定了他自己的政治前途 — — 而这场争夺两个中型反对党选票的战斗正逐渐演变成一场耗资数十亿美元的战斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/japan-upstart-party-has-37-billion-offer-to-back-prime-minister-ishiba-s-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 00:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈佛大学和芝加哥大学因学校考虑特朗普命令而警告教职员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/harvard-u-chicago-caution-faculty-as-schools-weigh-trump-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国大学正在试图解读特朗普政府的一项指令，该指令旨在暂停联邦拨款和贷款，这可能会扰乱高等教育资金，特别是对科学研究的资助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/harvard-u-chicago-caution-faculty-as-schools-weigh-trump-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 00:06:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>议员称英国国民医疗服务体系即使财政状况恶化仍自满</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/england-s-nhs-complacent-even-as-finances-deteriorate-mps-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个立法委员会表示，英国国家医疗服务体系 (NHS) 处于自满状态，改革陷入停滞，高级官员尚未准备好做出必要的根本性变革以修复不完善的国家医疗服务体系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/england-s-nhs-complacent-even-as-finances-deteriorate-mps-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普向拒绝亲自上班的联邦雇员提供买断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-offers-buyouts-to-federal-workers-who-want-to-work-from-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统正在向那些不愿意遵从他要求重返办公室的机构员工提供买断待遇，他希望在第二任期内重组联邦劳动力队伍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-offers-buyouts-to-federal-workers-who-want-to-work-from-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 23:10:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普支出暂停令引发混乱，随后遭阻挠</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-s-spending-halt-spawns-day-of-chaos-before-getting-blocked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统上任时承诺要振兴华盛顿。混乱的 24 小时让我们看到了特朗普的最终结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/trump-s-spending-halt-spawns-day-of-chaos-before-getting-blocked</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 22:58:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃伦敦促卢特尼克不要让不法之徒喜欢加密货币公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/warren-presses-lutnick-on-ties-to-crypto-firm-loved-by-outlaws</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党参议员伊丽莎白·沃伦 (Elizabeth Warren) 正在向商务部长提名人霍华德·卢特尼克 (Howard Lutnick) 施压，要求他说明自己及其公司 Cantor Fitzgerald LP 与一家犯罪世界首选加密货币公司之间的联系，并在周三的确认听证会之前提出有关潜在利益冲突的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/warren-presses-lutnick-on-ties-to-crypto-firm-loved-by-outlaws</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 16:40:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
